reviewText: Loved this DVD.  It was packaged appropriately and arrived in perfect conduction.  My fianc were hooked on the Vikings Series after viewing Season one.  Season two was even better and more exciting.  Thank you for making it available at such a reasonable price.  .
I love this show! What a great product. Arrived quickly.

Season two of the Vikings is a most critical season of the overall series, maybe that's why it is difficult to locate outside of Amazon.  After watching two episodes of Season one, we were hooked.  A most enjoyable and engrossing tale of Viking adventures and tales.  We have now completed viewing of all available seasons and find it hard to wait for any further seasons which may be in filming.  Excellent entertainment!
The case was damaged but the dvds work fine.
Killer good series. I'm buying each season as they come out.
My son loved it for Christmas present. Personally I haven't seen the series.
Bought as a gift and he loves it. Navy Veteran and we could not find Season 2 anywhere other than just purchasing this!
My favorite show! I am glad I own it now!
Bought as a Christmas gift and of course we love this show!
Superb Series, well done and great cast!
the promo states it had closed captioning. IT DOES NOT.  i find it impossible to understand the actors.  i love the series, but this product is worthless.
This will be a birthday present for my husband.  He loves this series.
Arrived fast and love the show.
Came on time, all I can really ask for.
Always enjoy new installments of the Vikings! Good drama and exciting imagery.
Vikings is a really good show. The DVD set that I got was of very high quality and reasonably priced.
Awesome series! Hope there are many more seasons to come. Seems fairly realistic from what a learned in history classes.
Awesome series... One of the best to date... Lots of action and twists. I wish I was a Viking.
Still going strong, this show does not dissapoint!  Strong plot development & very well done battles continue to entertain. Now with more aerial view.
Love the story, characters, history and scenery. History from the Viking perspective!!!! Obsessed
I was excited to get this set. I love the show & will enjoy watching Ragnar and all the others over & over.
Best series ever! Marathon watching time!
Great story. Great casting. Pretty much everything.

A great show honestly. I find myself scowling and disagreeing with some of the characters and rooting others on! Not to mention the lore and traditions it dives into. I'd recommend this for anyone who likes action and history thrown together!
I loved it, the characters, the action, the diverse points of view were so interesting! Travis Fimmel and his character actors in his Vikings family were unforgettable!
Only works in UK. Was not made clear when I purchased.

Fantastic movie, hard to stop watching.
Our son got hooked on it and one neighbor. Purchased all 4 seasons
